criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Able to understand verbal and written English language (due to resources, the adapted
             intervention will not be translated);

          -  ***To be on the waiting list for therapy at the Centre for Trauma Resilience and
             Growth, Nottingham UK***;

          -  Able to access a computer, CD player or mp3 file;

          -  Had experience of a traumatic event

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  participants involved in the pilot phase of the project

          -  unable to understand verbal and written English language
